dcterms:creator: M. Wang
D. Durante
R. E. Jung
D. B. Dunson
dcterms:description: The MRN-114 dataset records the structural connectivity among 68 brain regions for 114 individuals along with their Intelligence Quotient (IQ) scores, organized into an order-3 tensor where entries encode the presence or absence of fiber connections between brain regions across individuals.
dcterms:title: MRN-114 human brain connectivity data

dcterms:creator: A. Globerson
G. Chechik
F. Pereira
N. Tishby
dcterms:description: The NIPS dataset consists of word occurrence counts in papers published from 1987 to 2003, focusing on the top 100 authors and 200 most frequent words, normalized by log transformation with pseudo-count 1, resulting in an order-3 tensor with entries representing the log counts of words by authors across years.
dcterms:title: NIPS word occurrence data
